  "subject": "Fix gulp build",
  "commit_message": "Fix gulp build\n\n- rewrite gulpfile to not rely on the gulp-helpers dependency\n- remove the gulp-helpers dependency\n- update gulp (3.9.1 -> 4.0.0)\n- explicitly declare the d3-zoom and d3-force deps\n- declare missing maven-war-plugin version in pom\n- update snapshot version to 2.1.0-SNAPSHOT\n\nIssue-ID: AAI-4160\nChange-Id: Id05216512694be8cf5b0ac55f450d957fe784b5b\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
